    "description": "In Pool Ball Battle Royale, strategy and physics intertwine with Pool to create a gameplay experience like no other game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survival Mode</h2>Up to 8 players compete to be the last ball standing.  Players can be eliminated by falling into a hole, or flying off the board.  <br>Gravity wells pull players towards the holes with increasing strength. Will you be the last ball standing?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/ef9e3244bc365d0719d825e64181987b.poster.avif?t=1698541261\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/ef9e3244bc365d0719d825e64181987b.webm?t=1698541261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/ef9e3244bc365d0719d825e64181987b.mp4?t=1698541261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Crushing</h2>Land on top of other players to crush and eliminate them immediately<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/81c27c817a1980d4955a00cc9f910f73.poster.avif?t=1698541261\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/81c27c817a1980d4955a00cc9f910f73.webm?t=1698541261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/81c27c817a1980d4955a00cc9f910f73.mp4?t=1698541261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grappling Points</h2>Structures appear during play, each contains grappling points that you can briefly attach your ball to.  Use this added mobility to swing around the battlefield or land crushing blows on unsuspecting foes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/de0ae69e1e1fa7932b57d4c430bc4c5b.poster.avif?t=1698541261\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/de0ae69e1e1fa7932b57d4c430bc4c5b.webm?t=1698541261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/de0ae69e1e1fa7932b57d4c430bc4c5b.mp4?t=1698541261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Power-Up Balls</h2>Knock any Power-Up ball into a hole and absorbs its unique abilities<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Flame Ball </strong>- Shoot stunning flames and propel yourself<br></li><li> <strong>Anti Ball</strong> - Gain Momentum Into Collisions<br></li><li> <strong>Force Ball</strong> - Launch other players further<br></li><li> <strong>Ghost Ball</strong> - Only be visible to other players when close<br></li><li> <strong>Trailblazer Ball</strong> - Leave a collidable trail behind you </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/a3050621c365c2ae1559871ca4c03284.poster.avif?t=1698541261\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/a3050621c365c2ae1559871ca4c03284.webm?t=1698541261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/a3050621c365c2ae1559871ca4c03284.mp4?t=1698541261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plague Mode</h2>Survive against the odds in our Plague Mode. One ball begins as the infected, spreading disease upon contact. Will you emerge as the last bastion of health amidst the relentless contagion?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/51aed973ac2608742fe21e673be7189b.poster.avif?t=1698541261\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/51aed973ac2608742fe21e673be7189b.webm?t=1698541261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193040/extras/51aed973ac2608742fe21e673be7189b.mp4?t=1698541261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
